Next I read in the Case-Shiller data and kept only the necessary variables.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
hpi_data <- hpi_ids |>
  mutate(
    data = map(
      id,
      \(x) fredr(
        series_id = x,
        observation_start = ymd("2006-01-01"),
        observation_end = ymd("2023-12-31"),
        frequency = "m"
      )
    )
  ) |>
  select(-id) |>
  unnest(data) |>
  select(city, date, hpi = value)

gt(hpi_data[1:10, ])
```

